text: Night of Champions (2013) was a professional wrestling pay-per-view show made by WWE. It took place on September 15, 2013 at the Joe Louis Arena in Detroit, Michigan. It was the seventh Night of Champions event held by WWE. Similar to the last six events, the concept of the show was that every championship in the company was defended at the event. ==Results== === Tag Team Turmoil match === Order Team Elimination Eliminated by 1 3MB (Heath Slater and Drew McIntyre) (with Jinder Mahal) 1 Tons of Funk 2 Tons of Funk (Brodus Clay and Tensai) 2 The Real Americans 3 The Real Americans (Antonio Cesaro and Jack Swagger) (with Zeb Colter) 4 The Prime Time Players 4 The Usos (Jimmy and Jey Uso) 3 The Real Americans Winners The Prime Time Players (Darren Young and Titus O'Neil) Winners 11:14 ==References== ==Other websites== *Official Night of Champions 2013 website Category:2013 in professional wrestling Category:WWE Night of Champions Category:Sports in Detroit Category:2013 in the United States Category:2010s in Detroit Category:September 2013 events
